snippet: Bae Sang-moon of South Korea closed with a one-over-par 73, enough for a two-shot victory over Steven Bowditch (67) in the first event of the new PGA Tour season, the Frys.com Open in Napa, Calif.
abstract: Bae Sang-moon wins Frys.com Open golf tournament; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Bae Sang-moon of South Korea closed with a one-over-par 73, enough for a two-shot victory over Steven Bowditch (67) in the first event of the new PGA Tour season, the Frys.com Open in Napa, Calif.
